        <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <h1>About Smart Academy</h1>
        <p>Your gateway to mastering cutting-edge computer science technologies through comprehensive, hands-on courses designed by industry experts.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-book-reader"></i> Our Story</h2>
            <p>SMART ACADEMY was founded in 2018 with a simple mission: to make high-quality computer science education accessible to everyone, everywhere. What started as a small platform with a handful of courses has grown into a comprehensive learning ecosystem serving over 500,000 students worldwide.</p>
            <p>We believe that education should be engaging, practical, and directly applicable to real-world challenges. Our courses are designed not just to teach concepts, but to build skills that you can immediately put to use in your career or personal projects.</p>
            <p>Our team of instructors includes industry veterans from top tech companies, academic researchers, and passionate educators who are committed to your success.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Courses Section -->
    <section class="courses-section">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i> Our Course Offerings</h2>
        <div class="course-grid">
            <div class="course-card">
                <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                <h3>Artificial Intelligence</h3>
                <p>Dive into the world of AI with our comprehensive courses covering machine learning, deep learning, neural networks, and natural language processing.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="course-card">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                <h3>Cybersecurity</h3>
                <p>Master the art of protecting systems, networks, and programs from digital attacks. Our cybersecurity courses cover ethical hacking and security best practices.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="course-card">
                <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
                <h3>Software Engineering</h3>
                <p>Learn the principles of building robust, scalable software systems. Our curriculum covers software design patterns, architecture, and testing methodologies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="course-card">
                <i class="fas fa-paint-brush"></i>
                <h3>Front-End Development</h3>
                <p>Create stunning, responsive user interfaces with our front-end courses. Master HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, and modern frameworks.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="course-card">
                <i class="fas fa-server"></i>
                <h3>Back-End Development</h3>
                <p>Build the server-side logic that powers web applications. Learn Node.js, Python, and database management systems.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="course-card">
                <i class="fas fa-microchip"></i>
                <h3>Internet of Things (IoT)</h3>
                <p>Explore the interconnected world of smart devices. Our IoT courses cover sensor networks, embedded systems, and IoT security.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

